data.title: Jeremy Lynch - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Jeremy Lynch: his birthday, what he did before fame, his family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Football freestyler widely regarded as one of the best at what he does who joined Billy Wingrove to run the popular F2Freestylers - Ultimate Soccer Skills Channel on YouTube. One of his most popular comedic videos shows him recreating glitches from the video game FIFA in real life.

Before Fame

When he was 15, he dreamed of playing for Arsenal's Academy. He first started doing tricks with a soccer ball in 2000 after watching a Nike commercial with Edgar Davids and Denilson.

Trivia

He was featured in the documentary In the Hands of the Gods and was a finalist on Britain's Got Talent in 2008. He also plays the piano and has posted multiple videos asking his followers to send him song requests to his jeremylynchofficial Instagram account.

Family Life

He was born in London, England, UK. His mother's name is Jenny. He married Shauna Louise in 2021. In May 2023, they revealed they were expecting their first child together.
